@startuml
[*] --> CreatedAccount : user submits registration details
CreatedAccount --> RegisteredUser : system validates registration
RegisteredUser --> LoggedIn : login submitted and credentials valid
LoggedIn --> TicketStatus : user requests ticket status
LoggedIn --> BookingConfirmed : user submits booking request
BookingConfirmed --> PaymentMade : payment confirmed
LoggedIn --> AccountDetails : user requests account details
AccountDetails --> EditedAccount : user edits account details
AccountDetails --> DeletedAccount : user deletes account details
LoggedIn --> Logout : user completes action
@enduml
